727691f-a.title: Queens: Prince Street - 36th Road
727691f-a.text:
26 Prince Street, east side, north of 36th Road (formerly
Sylvester Street.). This was in 1873 a part of the Bloodgood
property. It was on the north side of Caleb W. Smith's house.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
